/*Subscriptions A new TV streaming service was recently started in Chefland called the Chef-TV.A group of N friends in Chefland want to buy Chef-TV subscriptions. We know that 6 people can share one Chef-TV subscription. Also, the cost of one Chef-TV subscription is X rupees. Determine the minimum total cost that the group of N friends will incur so that everyone in the group is able to use Chef-TV.*/

#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    int t,x,y,d;
    scanf("%d",&t);
    
    while (t--){
        scanf("%d %d",&x,&y);
        d=(x+5)/6.0;
        printf("%d\n",d*y);
        
    }
    
return 0;
}

